{"abstract":[{"text":"Automated macOS Setup Assistant sequences for headless VM provisioning.","type":"text"}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit\/SetupAutomation","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"topicSections":[{"anchor":"Type-Properties","title":"Type Properties","identifiers":["doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit\/SetupAutomation\/supportedVersions"],"generated":true},{"anchor":"Type-Methods","title":"Type Methods","identifiers":["doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit\/SetupAutomation\/isSupported(macOSVersion:)","doc:\/\/SpooktacularKit\/documentation\/SpooktacularKit\/SetupAutomation\/sequence(for:username:password:)"],"generated":true}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["macOS"],"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"enum"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"SetupAutomation"}]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"overview","text":"Overview"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"code":"SetupAutomation","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" provides version-specific keyboard input sequences"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"that walk through the macOS Setup Assistant without any human"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"interaction. After the sequence completes, the VM has:"}]},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"A user account (configurable, defaults to "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"admin"},{"type":"text","text":"\/"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"admin"},{"type":"text","text":")"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"SSH (Remote Login) enabled","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"A UTC timezone configured","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}]},{"anchor":"Design","type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Design"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"This follows the approach pioneered by","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"https:\/\/github.com\/cirruslabs\/tart","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" for Packer","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"boot_command"},{"text":" automation. The sequences have been verified against","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Tart’s working Packer plugin and adapted for direct use via the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Virtualization framework’s keyboard API.","type":"text"}]},{"anchor":"Requirements","type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Requirements"},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"A ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"VZVirtualMachineView"},{"text":" must be attached to the VM (even","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"offscreen) for keyboard events to reach the guest.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The VM must be freshly installed from an IPSW — previously","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"configured VMs will not show the Setup Assistant.","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Sequences are version-specific because Apple changes the Setup"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Assistant layout between major macOS releases."}]}]}]},{"anchor":"Example","type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Example"},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["guard SetupAutomation.isSupported(macOSVersion: 15) else {","    fatalError(\"No automation sequence for this version\")","}","","let steps = SetupAutomation.sequence(for: 15)","for step in steps {","    try await Task.sleep(for: .seconds(step.delay))","    await keyboardDriver.perform(step.action)","}"]},{"level":2,"text":"Adding Support for New macOS Versions","anchor":"Adding-Support-for-